WEBVTT

00:11.387 --> 00:12.997
<b>That was my stomach, sorry.</b>

00:14.427 --> 00:16.507
<b>What's your name?</b>

00:17.547 --> 00:18.687
<b>Denji!</b>

00:18.687 --> 00:21.007
<b>Let me be perfectly clear.</b>

00:21.357 --> 00:25.767
<b>From now on, you will be my dog.</b>

00:26.427 --> 00:28.737
<b>You may only answer me with "yes" or "woof."</b>

00:28.737 --> 00:30.757
<b>I have no use for a dog that says "no."</b>

00:32.027 --> 00:33.527
<b>What do you mean?</b>

00:33.527 --> 00:36.277
<b>I heard from a friend in Forensics</b>

00:36.797 --> 00:41.027
<b>that we euthanize dogs that are no longer useful.</b>

00:46.397 --> 00:48.617
<b><i>I thought she was kind.</i></b>

00:49.107 --> 00:51.307
<b><i>I fell for her a bit.</i></b>

00:51.307 --> 00:54.167
<b><i>I had no idea she was such a scary woman.</i></b>

00:54.167 --> 00:56.877
<b><i>She treats people like dogs.</i></b>

01:02.747 --> 01:05.347
<b><i>That's right. Pochita's dead.</i></b>

