01:09.657 --> 01:12.287
<b>We haven't had breakfast yet, either.</b>

01:12.287 --> 01:14.647
<b>Let's get something at the rest stop.</b>

01:15.057 --> 01:17.897
<b>Sorry, but I'm flat broke.</b>

01:18.257 --> 01:20.017
<b>Just tell me what you want.</b>

01:20.017 --> 01:21.687
<b>It's my treat.</b>

01:23.167 --> 01:25.907
<b>You'll draw too much attention if you're half-naked, so take this.</b>

01:28.877 --> 01:29.557
<b>Here.</b>

01:35.407 --> 01:39.597
<b><i>My whole life, people have called me dirty and smelly and avoided me.</i></b>

01:39.597 --> 01:41.927
<b><i>No one's ever treated me so kindly before.</i></b>

01:42.197 --> 01:44.627
<b><i>Certainly not a girl as pretty as her.</i></b>

01:48.047 --> 01:49.257
<b><i>I'm in love.</i></b>

01:53.287 --> 01:55.757
