01:55.757 --> 01:58.587
<b>Udon and... a hot dog!</b>

01:58.587 --> 01:59.637
<b>If that's all right?</b>

01:59.637 --> 02:00.767
<b>Sure.</b>

02:00.767 --> 02:02.857
<b>And a curry udon for me.</b>

02:02.857 --> 02:04.017
<b>Coming right up.</b>

02:04.017 --> 02:07.197
<b>Ah, curry udon sound goo—</b>

02:07.517 --> 02:08.697
<b>Oh, hello.</b>

02:09.277 --> 02:10.717
<b>Denji?</b>

02:10.717 --> 02:11.697
<b>Are you okay?</b>

02:11.697 --> 02:12.787
<b>Um...</b>

02:12.787 --> 02:14.537
<b>Smells good...</b>

02:14.537 --> 02:15.937
<b>How much is that?</b>

02:15.937 --> 02:17.667
<b>Just a moment.</b>

02:16.527 --> 02:17.667
<b>Denji.</b>

02:18.207 --> 02:19.797
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

02:18.207 --> 02:19.797
<b>That'll be 1,300 yen.</b>

02:19.797 --> 02:22.907
<b>The chainsaws cut me up as well.</b>

02:22.907 --> 02:24.217
<b>Here. Keep the change.</b>

02:22.907 --> 02:26.207
<b>I must've lost a little too much blood.</b>

02:26.807 --> 02:29.217
<b>How did you become like this?</b>

02:29.747 --> 02:32.967
<b>My pet devil became my heart.</b>

02:34.087 --> 02:35.717
<b>Hard to believe, I know.</b>

02:36.077 --> 02:38.447
<b>I don't want to believe it either.</b>

02:38.447 --> 02:41.267
<b>Pochita gave his life to save me...</b>

02:45.767 --> 02:50.487
<b>Your condition is almost without precedent.</b>

02:51.217 --> 02:54.237
<b>In fact, it's so uncommon that there's no word for it.</b>

02:55.827 --> 02:58.187
<b>I believe you, though.</b>

03:00.147 --> 03:02.997
<b>I have an especially keen sense of smell.</b>

03:03.517 --> 03:04.737
<b>That's why I can tell.</b>

03:06.097 --> 03:09.087
<b>Your friend is alive inside of you.</b>

03:09.417 --> 03:11.217
<b>And I don't mean that in any poetic sense.</b>

03:11.667 --> 03:15.477
<b>Your body gives off both the scent of a human and that of a devil.</b>

03:16.527 --> 03:17.727
<b>Really?</b>

03:17.727 --> 03:18.977
<b>Wow.</b>

03:18.977 --> 03:21.337
<b>I'm so hap—</b>

03:29.137 --> 03:29.877
<b>Udon!</b>

03:31.797 --> 03:32.497
<b>Udon?</b>

03:38.997 --> 03:41.117
<b>Can I eat my udon now?</b>

03:41.457 --> 03:42.127
<b>Yeah.</b>

03:42.647 --> 03:44.127
<b>Are sure you're okay?</b>

03:44.127 --> 03:45.377
<b>Can you eat it on your own?</b>

03:45.377 --> 03:46.457
<b>I ca—</b>

03:48.407 --> 03:49.877
<b>I can't.</b>

03:50.177 --> 03:52.157
<b>Say, "Ah!"</b>

03:52.157 --> 03:53.127
<b>Ah!</b>

03:55.107 --> 03:56.097
<b>Do you like it?</b>

03:56.097 --> 03:56.887
<b>Woof!</b>

03:57.257 --> 04:00.377
<b>Most people would turn their nose up at soggy udon.</b>

04:00.377 --> 04:02.137
<b>What a good boy you are.</b>

04:02.427 --> 04:04.017
<b>You really are quite like a dog.</b>

04:07.467 --> 04:10.347
<b>So, what's your name?</b>

04:11.707 --> 04:12.647
<b>Makima.</b>

04:13.067 --> 04:14.197
<b>Makima?</b>

04:14.647 --> 04:18.137
<b>D-Do you have a type when it comes to men?</b>

04:18.137 --> 04:19.657
<b>Hmm...</b>

04:24.757 --> 04:27.087
<b>Someone like this Denji guy, I'd say.</b>

04:27.987 --> 04:29.107
<b>Denji?</b>

04:30.657 --> 04:31.307
<b>Huh?</b>

04:32.757 --> 04:33.737
<b>Me?</b>

04:42.687 --> 04:45.437
<b><i>Do you have a type when it comes to men?</i></b>

04:45.437 --> 04:47.017
<b><i>Someone like this Denji guy, I'd say.</i></b>

04:47.017 --> 04:47.107
<b><i>Someone like this Denji guy, I'd say.</i></b>

04:49.587 --> 04:52.487
<b>I love you too, Makima.</b>

04:54.217 --> 04:55.297
<b>Denji!</b>

04:55.297 --> 04:56.647
<b>This way!</b>

04:59.007 --> 05:01.807
<b>This is the Tokyo HQ for the Bureau's devil hunters.</b>

05:06.347 --> 05:11.527
<b>If you include civilians, there are over a thousand devil hunters in Tokyo,</b>

05:11.527 --> 05:15.917
<b>but the {Public Safety}Bureau offers a lot of paid vacation time and the best benefits by far.</b>

05:19.287 --> 05:22.267
<b><i>If Makima's into me,</i></b>

05:22.677 --> 05:26.787
<b><i>then there's a chance we could become a couple if we keep working together.</i></b>

05:27.767 --> 05:29.767
<b><i>And if we become a couple,</i></b>

05:29.767 --> 05:32.527
<b><i>we can do couple things together.</i></b>

05:32.527 --> 05:33.557
<b><i>I wanna do it so bad!</i></b>

05:33.557 --> 05:35.777
<b><i>I wanna do the thing that couples do!</i></b>

05:38.767 --> 05:40.027
<b>Denji.</b>

05:40.447 --> 05:41.277
<b>Yes?</b>

05:42.027 --> 05:44.787
<b>We have a uniform, so put this on.</b>

05:45.307 --> 05:47.907
<b>Once you've changed, I'll introduce you to one of your coworkers.</b>

05:55.707 --> 05:58.337
<b>This is Hayakawa Aki.</b>

05:58.337 --> 06:00.597
<b>He's been working here for three years.</b>

06:01.147 --> 06:03.607
<b>Tag along with him for the day.</b>

06:03.607 --> 06:04.097
<b>Huh?!</b>

06:04.647 --> 06:07.327
<b>I'm not going to work with you?!</b>

06:07.857 --> 06:09.347
<b>Of course you're not.</b>

06:09.717 --> 06:12.427
<b>You're nowhere near her league.</b>

06:12.427 --> 06:13.427
<b>We're going out on patrol.</b>

06:13.427 --> 06:14.377
<b>No!</b>

06:14.377 --> 06:16.107
<b>Makima!</b>

06:16.997 --> 06:18.547
<b>Hey! Get up!</b>

06:18.547 --> 06:19.657
<b>No way!</b>

06:19.657 --> 06:22.097
<b>I wanna work with Makima.</b>

06:24.847 --> 06:27.387
<b>You could work with me,</b>

06:27.387 --> 06:29.217
<b>if you can prove you can do a good job.</b>

06:38.227 --> 06:40.127
<b>So show me what you can do, okay?</b>

06:47.727 --> 06:49.637
<b>Hey, Aki.</b>

06:50.217 --> 06:52.647
<b>Does Makima have a boyfriend?</b>

06:56.497 --> 06:57.507
<b>Hello?</b>

06:59.577 --> 07:00.027
<b>Tell me!</b>

07:01.147 --> 07:02.277
<b>Come with me.</b>

07:28.277 --> 07:29.637
<b>Quit this job.</b>

07:30.727 --> 07:33.037
<b>If you show up tomorrow, 
I'll beat the crap out of you again.</b>

07:33.787 --> 07:34.897
<b>Why?</b>

07:36.177 --> 07:38.647
<b>Can't you see I'm doing you a favor?</b>

07:39.357 --> 07:42.327
<b>If you're not serious about this job, 
you'll be dead in no time.</b>

07:42.327 --> 07:46.407
<b>Everyone I've worked with who came for the paycheck is now dead.</b>

07:46.407 --> 07:48.657
<b>Killed by devils, all of them.</b>

07:49.287 --> 07:53.397
<b>The only ones who're still alive are those with deep convictions.</b>

07:54.587 --> 07:55.607
<b>And let me guess...</b>

07:56.207 --> 07:58.797
<b>You only took this job to get close to Makima, right?</b>

07:59.127 --> 08:00.717
<b>Bingo.</b>

08:01.627 --> 08:04.217
<b>Then I was right to beat you up.</b>

08:08.557 --> 08:10.917
<b>I'll explain things to Makima.</b>

08:11.387 --> 08:14.077
<b>How you got scared of a devil and ran away.</b>

08:28.637 --> 08:31.907
<b>You're too nice, man.</b>

08:32.427 --> 08:36.667
<b>When <i>I</i> fight a dude,</b>

08:36.917 --> 08:40.157
<b>I only go for the balls!</b>

08:47.357 --> 08:49.977
<b>Today, I ate udon for the first time.</b>

08:50.697 --> 08:52.807
<b>And a hot dog too.</b>

08:52.807 --> 08:55.387
<b>I was treated like a person for the first time.</b>

08:55.387 --> 08:57.677
<b>Someone bought me a meal for the first time.</b>

08:58.317 --> 09:01.187
<b>To me, this is like a dream come true.</b>

09:01.797 --> 09:05.947
<b>I'm not very serious about being a devil hunter. You're right.</b>

09:06.357 --> 09:08.817
<b>But if it means I can keep living like this,</b>

09:09.567 --> 09:11.247
<b>I don't even care if it gets me killed.</b>

09:12.867 --> 09:14.847
<b>Actually, I take that back.</b>

09:15.677 --> 09:17.577
<b>This life isn't just mine anymore.</b>

09:22.817 --> 09:24.217
<b>You want Makima?</b>

09:25.167 --> 09:29.637
<b>No way she'd fall for a lowlife like you.</b>

09:29.637 --> 09:30.387
<b>What?!</b>

09:30.627 --> 09:31.637
<b>Screw you!</b>

09:31.637 --> 09:34.557
<b>You just have a thing for her too!</b>

09:39.787 --> 09:42.357
<b>You really do...</b>

09:43.587 --> 09:45.727
<b>only go for...</b>

09:45.727 --> 09:47.857
<b>the balls...</b>

09:53.457 --> 09:54.787
<b>Shit.</b>

09:56.907 --> 10:00.627
<b>The Balls Devil got his balls.</b>

10:01.167 --> 10:02.437
<b>That's a lie.</b>

10:02.437 --> 10:04.167
<b>He's lying.</b>

10:04.447 --> 10:06.667
<b>Okay, what do you think?</b>

10:06.667 --> 10:08.677
<b>Can you two work together?</b>

10:08.677 --> 10:09.707
<b>No freakin' way.</b>

10:09.707 --> 10:11.297
<b>He's total scum.</b>

10:11.567 --> 10:13.857
<b>I'm glad to see you're getting along.</b>

10:14.587 --> 10:17.557
<b>Denji, you will be joining Hayakawa's unit.</b>

10:17.867 --> 10:18.867
<b>Unit?</b>

10:18.867 --> 10:20.807
<b>This lowlife?!</b>

10:20.807 --> 10:24.267
<b>We already have enough troublemakers as it is.</b>

10:24.267 --> 10:26.427
<b>We can't afford to take any more weirdos.</b>

10:26.427 --> 10:29.087
<b>Remember what I told you when I formed the unit?</b>

10:29.087 --> 10:33.187
<b>It's meant to be experimental, rather than conform to standards and conventions.</b>

10:35.837 --> 10:38.077
<b>Who is this guy, anyway?</b>

10:38.357 --> 10:42.307
<b>He's a human, but he can also turn into a devil.</b>

10:42.307 --> 10:44.347
<b>You gotta admit, pretty awesome, hey?!</b>

10:44.347 --> 10:46.197
<b>You're not pulling my leg, are you?</b>

10:46.197 --> 10:50.417
<b>I've only heard vague rumors about such a thing.</b>

10:50.417 --> 10:52.717
<b>Denji is special.</b>

10:53.327 --> 10:57.977
<b>So he's getting special treatment.</b>

10:58.257 --> 11:02.087
<b>If he quits the Bureau or commits any offense,</b>

11:02.087 --> 11:05.067
<b>he will be treated as a devil and eliminated.</b>

11:05.907 --> 11:06.727
<b>Huh?</b>

11:07.177 --> 11:09.987
<b>What do you mean?</b>

11:10.557 --> 11:13.537
<b>I mean that we'll be working together until the day you die.</b>

11:17.397 --> 11:20.497
<b>It was decided that you'll live with me 
so I can keep an eye on you.</b>

11:21.357 --> 11:24.497
<b>And don't forget, I have permission to kill you if you run away.</b>

11:31.177 --> 11:34.257
<b>So, do you think Makima is a bad person?</b>

11:34.757 --> 11:37.387
<b>If you think she is, then give up on her.</b>

11:37.787 --> 11:39.507
<b>If you're a devil,</b>

11:39.507 --> 11:41.387
<b>just be grateful she's letting you live.</b>

11:41.877 --> 11:44.397
<b>After all, we're devil hunters.</b>

11:44.747 --> 11:46.797
<b>So, is she a good person?</b>

11:46.797 --> 11:48.437
<b>Of course she is.</b>

11:49.967 --> 11:52.407
<b>She saved my life.</b>

12:02.347 --> 12:03.957
<b>Makima...</b>

12:04.587 --> 12:06.797
<b>I wanna feel her warm embrace again.</b>

12:07.267 --> 12:08.707
<b>What?!</b>

12:08.707 --> 12:08.797
<b>What?!</b>

12:10.797 --> 12:14.797
<b>Strawberry jam, ume jam, orange marmalade,</b>

12:15.117 --> 12:18.267
<b>butter and honey, and...</b>

12:18.267 --> 12:20.557
<b>I'll throw some cinnamon on too.</b>

12:20.807 --> 12:23.807
<b>This is now the ultimate slice of toast.</b>

12:26.607 --> 12:27.937
<b>Hell yeah!</b>

12:29.007 --> 12:31.187
<b>Sooo freakin' good!</b>

12:41.217 --> 12:42.367
<b>Don't stay in there too long!</b>

12:44.987 --> 12:46.827
<b>Don't sleep on the toilet!</b>

12:57.137 --> 12:59.597
<b>A fiend has been sighted at a residential building in west Nerima.</b>

13:00.427 --> 13:02.167
<b>All civilians have been evacuated,</b>

13:02.167 --> 13:04.347
<b>and a perimeter has been established.</b>

13:05.007 --> 13:08.367
<b>The target fiend is holed up in a room on the second floor.</b>

13:08.367 --> 13:10.427
<b>We'll let you guys take it from here.</b>

13:10.427 --> 13:13.357
<b>Hayakawa, is that a new recruit you've got there?</b>

13:17.897 --> 13:19.867
<b>By the way, what's a fiend?</b>

13:20.187 --> 13:23.667
<b>What? Did you not go to school or something?</b>

13:23.667 --> 13:25.407
<b>No, actually.</b>

13:27.527 --> 13:31.227
<b>A devil that has taken over a human's corpse—that's a fiend.</b>

13:31.227 --> 13:32.277
<b>Hmm...</b>

13:33.677 --> 13:36.207
<b>Wait, does that mean I'm a fiend too?</b>

13:36.207 --> 13:39.887
<b>You can easily recognize a fiend by how their head looks.</b>

13:40.177 --> 13:42.887
<b>You'll understand when you see it.</b>

13:49.747 --> 13:51.987
<b>A fiend still has the character of a devil.</b>

13:51.987 --> 13:53.857
<b>You kill this one.</b>

13:54.377 --> 13:56.487
<b>Turn into a devil, and show me what you've got.</b>

13:56.827 --> 13:59.307
<b>Then I'll decide if you can be useful or not.</b>

13:59.857 --> 14:01.237
<b>Don't look!</b>

14:01.487 --> 14:04.237
<b>You're dead! Dead! Dead!</b>

14:04.237 --> 14:06.247
<b>You filthy devil hunters!</b>

14:14.437 --> 14:17.967
<b>Hold on, why didn't you use your devil powers?</b>

14:18.217 --> 14:23.137
<b>Well, when I use my power to kill devils,</b>

14:23.137 --> 14:24.717
<b>it looks really painful.</b>

14:25.007 --> 14:30.977
<b>You see, I could've ended up a fiend like him,</b>

14:31.397 --> 14:35.357
<b>so... I kinda wanted to give him a quick and painless death.</b>

14:36.987 --> 14:38.657
<b>Listen here, punk.</b>

14:39.197 --> 14:40.947
<b>A fiend is still a devil.</b>

14:41.447 --> 14:43.867
<b>As a devil hunter, you shouldn't show them any sympathy.</b>

14:44.467 --> 14:48.117
<b>My entire family was killed by a devil, 
right before my eyes.</b>

