14:56.367 --> 14:58.617
<b>You're the only one here who's not taking this seriously.</b>

14:57.367 --> 15:00.367


14:59.117 --> 15:02.637
<b>I want to kill devils in the most painful way possible.</b>

15:03.327 --> 15:04.527
<b>And you?</b>

15:04.527 --> 15:06.887
<b>You want to be friends with them?</b>

15:08.847 --> 15:11.397
<b>Sure, if there's a devil who wants to be my friend, I'm down.</b>

15:12.697 --> 15:14.447
<b>After all, I don't have any friends.</b>

15:18.817 --> 15:21.377
<b>I'm going to remember you said that.</b>

15:30.457 --> 15:32.417
<b>Man, that made him snap.</b>

15:32.717 --> 15:36.197
<b>I actually just didn't wanna get blood on these porno mags.</b>

15:36.667 --> 15:40.427
<b>If I brought the chainsaws out, they'd be soaked right now.</b>

15:40.897 --> 15:44.467
<b>In return for giving you a quick death, 
I'm taking these, all right?</b>

15:49.717 --> 15:50.757
<b>Sweet!</b>

15:50.757 --> 15:51.937
<b>It's the good stuff.</b>

15:52.447 --> 15:55.227
<b>Let me see your dreams come true.{ep01@16:24 minus its starting "In exchange"}</b>

15:55.537 --> 15:58.477
<b>I'm serious too, Pochita.</b>

15:58.927 --> 16:02.237
<b>I'm living out my dreams, just like our contract says.</b>

16:02.867 --> 16:04.987
<b><i>I'm going to remember you said that.</i></b>

16:05.507 --> 16:08.907
<b>My dreams have already come true,</b>

16:08.907 --> 16:10.747
<b>but he's still chasing his.</b>

16:13.287 --> 16:15.407
<b><i>I can take a bath every day.</i></b>

16:15.407 --> 16:17.077
<b><i>I can eat good stuff.</i></b>

16:17.077 --> 16:19.377
<b><i>I have a pretty girl near me.</i></b>

16:19.877 --> 16:22.047
<b><i>My life's already 10 outta 10.</i></b>

16:22.547 --> 16:24.487
<b><i>Even so, it feels like something's missing.</i></b>

16:24.927 --> 16:28.387
<b><i>Do I have something else? Like a serious goal?</i></b>

16:28.687 --> 16:31.447
<b><i>For him, it must be something to do with revenge.</i></b>

16:31.447 --> 16:33.647
<b><i>For those guys, it's to protect their families.</i></b>

16:36.757 --> 16:38.827
<b><i>I wonder if Makima has something like that.</i></b>

16:39.887 --> 16:41.397
<b><i>Makima...</i></b>

16:42.597 --> 16:45.657
<b><i>Boobs! I wanna touch some boobs!</i></b>

16:51.487 --> 16:54.777
<b><i>I gave up a long time ago, 
'cause I didn't have a chance in hell.</i></b>

16:54.777 --> 16:58.037
<b><i>But now that I've got proper a job, 
it's a different story.</i></b>

16:58.777 --> 17:01.577
<b><i>My chances of going all the way are still slim, though,</i></b>

17:02.267 --> 17:03.547
<b><i>but if it's just boobs...</i></b>

17:04.597 --> 17:07.927
<b><i>With a little confidence and determination, 
I could be fondling boobs.</i></b>

17:08.397 --> 17:10.727
<b><i>You're the only one here who's not taking this seriously.</i></b>

17:10.727 --> 17:12.427
<b><i>Now I get it.</i></b>

17:13.237 --> 17:15.977
<b><i>I found the thing that'll push me to be serious!</i></b>

17:16.347 --> 17:18.127
<b><i>My goal!</i></b>

17:18.127 --> 17:19.227
<b><i>It's...</i></b>

17:19.597 --> 17:20.727
<b><i>boobs!</i></b>

17:21.227 --> 17:22.357
<b>Boobs?</b>

17:22.617 --> 17:25.227
<b>Hey! Pay attention, moron!</b>

17:25.227 --> 17:26.107
<b>What?</b>

17:26.387 --> 17:29.617
<b>I am assigning you a partner, starting now.</b>

17:30.137 --> 17:31.267
<b>A partner?</b>

17:31.267 --> 17:34.247
<b>The Bureau's rules are that for small-scale missions and patrols,</b>

17:34.567 --> 17:38.997
<b>agents must work in teams of two, 
for safety reasons.</b>

17:39.537 --> 17:42.127
<b>Great timing. That's her now.</b>

17:43.267 --> 17:44.907
<b>Be careful, though.</b>

17:44.907 --> 17:46.257
<b>She's a fiend.</b>

17:47.727 --> 17:48.977
<b>Listen here!</b>

17:48.977 --> 17:50.517
<b>Prostrate yourself before me, human!</b>

17:50.517 --> 17:52.397
<b>My name is Power!</b>

17:52.397 --> 17:54.407
<b>Are you to be my partner?</b>

17:55.417 --> 17:57.527
<b>Power? Your name's "Power"?!</b>

17:57.527 --> 17:58.767
<b>And you're a fiend?!</b>

17:59.337 --> 18:02.207
<b>Is a fiend really working as a devil hunter?!</b>

18:05.557 --> 18:06.927
<b>Ah, what the hell.</b>

18:06.927 --> 18:08.187
<b>Let's work together!</b>

18:09.277 --> 18:12.537
<b>Under normal circumstances, 
fiends are to be eliminated just like devils,</b>

18:12.817 --> 18:15.127
<b>but Power is rather reasonable,</b>

18:15.127 --> 18:17.287
<b>so I had her join Hayakawa's unit.</b>

18:17.887 --> 18:19.487
<b>As I mentioned before,</b>

18:19.487 --> 18:22.897
<b>the Public Safety Bureau's Fourth Special Anti-Devil Division is an experimental unit.</b>

18:23.317 --> 18:28.547
<b>The higher-ups could disband it at any time, 
if it doesn't produce results.</b>

18:28.907 --> 18:32.797
<b>And you know what would happen to the two of you then, right?</b>

18:34.057 --> 18:35.057
<b>Yataba Photography</b>

