19:30.497 --> 19:32.447
<b>There's no freakin' devils here!</b>

19:31.607 --> 19:34.607


19:32.697 --> 19:35.657
<b>Probably my fault.</b>

19:35.657 --> 19:39.707
<b>Before I became a fiend, 
I was a much-feared devil.</b>

19:40.337 --> 19:43.287
<b>Small fry flee the moment they catch a whiff of my scent.</b>

19:43.287 --> 19:46.087
<b>Wait, what?! How're we supposed to deliver results, then?!</b>

19:47.577 --> 19:50.967
<b><i>If you have any questions, direct them to Hayakawa.</i></b>

19:51.727 --> 19:53.717
<b><i>He's the one who decided to partner you two up.</i></b>

19:54.127 --> 19:57.097
<b><i>That bastard set me up!</i></b>

19:57.557 --> 20:00.557
<b><i>He stuck me with Power so I won't have a chance to show 'em what I can do.</i></b>

20:00.557 --> 20:03.097
<b><i>He's trying to make me quit!</i></b>

20:06.257 --> 20:07.977
<b>That's the smell of blood!</b>

20:09.687 --> 20:11.267
<b>Hey, wait a sec!</b>

20:11.267 --> 20:12.197
<b>Where're you going?</b>

20:16.027 --> 20:18.197
<b>A fight! A fight!</b>

20:18.197 --> 20:20.067
<b>To battle!</b>

20:20.067 --> 20:21.037
<b>Damn, she's quick!</b>

20:21.307 --> 20:24.787
<b>Civilians have been evacuated, 
and a perimeter's been established.</b>

20:25.087 --> 20:27.667
<b>It's the Sea Cucumber Devil. 
I repeat, the Sea Cucumber Devil.</b>

20:27.927 --> 20:30.407
<b>Requesting backup at Nerima Station.</b>

20:30.407 --> 20:32.497
<b>No, I said sea cucumber.</b>

20:32.497 --> 20:34.387
<b>You know what a sea cucumber is, right?</b>

20:34.387 --> 20:36.827
<b>What? No, I told you—</b>

20:41.597 --> 20:43.017
<b>Sea cucumber...</b>

20:43.417 --> 20:44.767
<b>Behold!</b>

20:45.027 --> 20:47.007
<b>My accomplishment!</b>

